<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- bḥr mḥbẗ ạlfạdy .. lạ yḥd
 mtsʿ ạlạ̉rjạʾ
 fy ṭwlh wʿmqh .. srmdyuⁿ
 wmạ lh ạstqṣạʾ
 ạlqrạr- qd fạq ḥbh .. qd zạd fḍlh
 ạ̹dẖ jʿlny .. hyklaⁿạ lrwḥh
 gẖdwt wạrtẖaⁿạ .. llh fy ạlmsyḥ
 wtrnmt sẖftạy .. bạltsbyḥ
 (kl mạ ly fy ạlḥyạẗ .. kl ʿmry llmmạt)2
 llḥbyb llḥbyb .. mn fdạny bạlṣlyb
 2- bmwth tlạqy̱ .. ʿly̱ ạlṣlyb
 ạlbr wạlslạm
 bnṣrẗ ạlqyạmẗ .. sẖmsuⁿ ạ̉ḍạʾt
 flạsẖt ạlẓlạm
 3- blṭfh ạlʿjyb .. sby̱ fw̉ạdy
 ạ̉zạl ḥmạ̉ty
 ạ̉ḍḥy̱ kdẖạ mjny .. trs kẖlạṣy
 ynbwʿ nṣrty</lyrics>
<title>bḥr mḥbẗ ạlfạdy</title>
<hymn_number>620</hymn_number>
<author>nạjy fw̉ạd</author>
</song>